00:44:19,880 --> 00:44:20,440
 onaj čovjek

848
00:44:20,440 --> 00:44:22,420
 i rekao je

849
00:44:22,420 --> 00:44:22,820
 Isusu

850
00:44:22,820 --> 00:44:24,420
 molio sam tvoje učenike

851
00:44:24,420 --> 00:44:25,440
 da mi izlječe sina,

852
00:44:25,440 --> 00:44:26,640
 ali nisu uspjeli,

853
00:44:26,640 --> 00:44:27,360
 možeš li mi ti?

854
00:44:27,360 --> 00:44:27,680
 Znači,

855
00:44:27,680 --> 00:44:29,320
 legenda je jako inteligentanska.

856
00:44:29,320 --> 00:44:30,340
 Proviša učenici

857
00:44:30,340 --> 00:44:30,760
 ma vjerojatnost

858
00:44:30,760 --> 00:44:31,600
 bili dostupniji.

859
00:44:32,500 --> 00:44:33,300
 Oni nisu uspjeli

860
00:44:33,300 --> 00:44:33,740
 i on kaže

861
00:44:33,740 --> 00:44:34,020
 dobro,

862
00:44:34,020 --> 00:44:34,740
 vi ne možete

863
00:44:34,740 --> 00:44:35,980
 idan ja vašem šefu.

864
00:44:35,980 --> 00:44:37,380
 On će siguro moći

865
00:44:37,380 --> 00:44:38,140
 kad vam je on dao

866
00:44:38,140 --> 00:44:38,700
 taj autoritet.

867
00:44:38,700 --> 00:44:40,200
 I Isus dolazi

868
00:44:40,200 --> 00:44:41,700
 i Isus lakoće

869
00:44:41,700 --> 00:44:42,580
 vam ozdravi sina.

870
00:44:42,580 --> 00:44:45,000
 I ono što on rekao

871
00:44:45,000 --> 00:44:47,460
 kad su ga učenici

872
00:44:47,460 --> 00:44:47,840
 pitali,

873
00:44:47,840 --> 00:44:49,080
 zašto mi to nismo uspjeli

874
00:44:49,080 --> 00:44:49,880
 a ti si uspio,

875
00:44:49,880 --> 00:44:51,320
 a dao si nam autoritet.

876
00:44:51,320 --> 00:44:53,400
 On kaže,

877
00:44:53,900 --> 00:44:54,820
 zbog nevjere.

878
00:44:54,820 --> 00:44:58,560
 I ovaj post,

879
00:44:58,560 --> 00:45:01,480
 očito je bio takav duhovni uzrok,

880
00:45:01,480 --> 00:45:03,620
 se pobjeđuje postom i molitvom.

881
00:45:03,620 --> 00:45:08,060
 A post nije metoda

882
00:45:08,060 --> 00:45:12,960
 i post nije neka disciplina

883
00:45:12,960 --> 00:45:15,020
 i neka stvar koju odraziš,

884
00:45:15,020 --> 00:45:16,900
 pa legalistički zaslužiš neki autoritet.

885
00:45:18,500 --> 00:45:22,260
 Post je neki oblik molitve

886
00:45:22,260 --> 00:45:25,840
 kojim ti izražaš Bogu.

887
00:45:25,840 --> 00:45:27,540
 Ovo mi je sad važnije od tebe,

888
00:45:27,540 --> 00:45:29,080
 od važnijam je,

889
00:45:29,080 --> 00:45:34,300
 važniji si mi ti nego hrana

890
00:45:34,300 --> 00:45:37,220
 i radim svjesno ovo trpljenje

891
00:45:37,220 --> 00:45:38,560
 da mogu biti više s tobom

892
00:45:38,560 --> 00:45:40,000
 i o sve što sam pričao.

893
00:45:40,000 --> 00:45:40,860
 Post te izvaja

894
00:45:40,860 --> 00:45:43,600
 i Bog može puno više raditi s tobom.

895
00:45:43,600 --> 00:45:45,180
 To znači da njegovi apostoli

896
00:45:45,180 --> 00:45:46,420
 nisu ušli dovoljno

897
00:45:46,420 --> 00:45:48,240
 u samodisciplinu

898
00:45:48,240 --> 00:45:50,900
 u autoritet,

899
00:45:50,900 --> 00:45:52,720
 u razlučivanje

900
00:45:52,720 --> 00:45:55,960
 i sve ono što post izgrađuje u čovjeku.

901
00:45:55,960 --> 00:45:58,960
 I ako se pitate zašto ste duhovno slabi

902
00:45:58,960 --> 00:46:02,060
 i nemate pobjedu nad područjima svoga života

903
00:46:02,060 --> 00:46:04,420
 gdje ste kušani, gdje padate,

904
00:46:04,420 --> 00:46:07,400
 najčešće nema molitve i posta.

905
00:46:07,400 --> 00:46:13,040
 I ako želite znati kako biti pobjedonosni

906
00:46:13,040 --> 00:46:14,460
 u svom duhovnom životu,

907
00:46:14,460 --> 00:46:16,340
 onda molite i postite.

908
00:46:17,980 --> 00:46:21,880
 i apostoli su sigurno naučili

909
00:46:21,880 --> 00:46:23,100
 vrijednu, vrijednu lekciju.

910
00:46:23,100 --> 00:46:25,580
 A to znači da Isus uvijek bio potpuno

911
00:46:25,580 --> 00:46:26,860
 u autoritetu,

912
00:46:26,860 --> 00:46:28,040
 u molitvi i u postu.

913
00:46:28,040 --> 00:46:31,100
 Imao je takav odnos gospodino.

914
00:46:31,100 --> 00:46:32,020
 Isus je,

915
00:46:32,020 --> 00:46:33,560
 kad ja kad sam čita šta ono,

916
00:46:33,560 --> 00:46:35,440
 med i mlijeko je legenda jeo.

917
00:46:35,440 --> 00:46:39,440
 Ja predpostavljam Isus jeo tako malo,

918
00:46:39,440 --> 00:46:41,080
 koliko mu je potrebno za život.

919
00:46:41,320 --> 00:46:42,880
 Ja vjerujem da on uživa o hrani,

920
00:46:42,880 --> 00:46:45,540
 ali je jeo koliko mu je bilo potrebno

921
00:46:45,540 --> 00:46:49,480
 i jeo je zato da održi svoje zdravlje,

922
00:46:49,480 --> 00:46:52,200
 održi snagu i sve ono što ide s tim.

923
00:46:52,340 --> 00:46:53,460
 Šovjek jeo i ja njetinu

924
00:46:53,460 --> 00:46:54,400
 na posljednjoj večer.

925
00:46:54,400 --> 00:47:01,480
 Ovo je jako važno duhovno načelo.

926
00:47:01,480 --> 00:47:03,700
 Ako niste negdje pobjedonosni,

927
00:47:03,700 --> 00:47:06,220
 vrlo vjerojatno ne molite i ne postite.

928
00:47:07,340 --> 00:47:10,920
 A Bog u svakom trenutku vašeg života

929
00:47:10,920 --> 00:47:12,520
 poziva vas na molitvu i post.

930
00:47:12,520 --> 00:47:13,740
 U svakom trenutku.

931
00:47:13,740 --> 00:47:15,500
 On vas poziva bliže sebi.

932
00:47:15,500 --> 00:47:17,820
 I to su redovni načini

933
00:47:17,820 --> 00:47:19,580
 kako mi možemo doći bliže njemu.

934
00:47:19,580 --> 00:47:20,700
 Kroz molitvu i post.

935
00:47:20,700 --> 00:47:22,660
 I znate, molitva je razgovor s Bogom.

936
00:47:22,660 --> 00:47:24,660
 To je ona osnovno školska definicija.

937
00:47:24,660 --> 00:47:27,800
 Tim molitvom i postom dolaziš njemu

938
00:47:27,800 --> 00:47:28,220
 i govoriš mu,

939
00:47:28,220 --> 00:47:30,600
 sad želim tebe ovoj vrijeme za tebe, za nas.

940
00:47:30,600 --> 00:47:32,480
 Govori sluga tvoj, sluša.

941
00:47:32,480 --> 00:47:33,820
 Ti imaš ješt života vječnog.

942
00:47:33,820 --> 00:47:36,180
 Izdvajam se iz duha svijeta.

943
00:47:36,260 --> 00:47:37,280
 Izdvajam se iz svega.

944
00:47:37,280 --> 00:47:39,100
 Staljam svakodnevno sve sa strane.

945
00:47:39,100 --> 00:47:40,660
 I želim sad provjeti vrijeme

946
00:47:40,660 --> 00:47:41,800
 s tovo i ovako ušimaš.

947
00:47:41,800 --> 00:47:45,260
 I kad sam čitao dokumente

948
00:47:45,260 --> 00:47:46,580
 drugog Vatikanskog sabora,

949
00:47:46,580 --> 00:47:48,700
 to sam već pričao

950
00:47:48,700 --> 00:47:49,580
 i to ću uvijek pričao

951
00:47:49,580 --> 00:47:50,440
 da do kraja života,

952
00:47:50,440 --> 00:47:51,720
 šokirala me jedna stvar

953
00:47:51,720 --> 00:47:54,420
 i onda sam maltretirao ekipu u uredu.

954
00:47:54,420 --> 00:47:59,160
 Drugi Vatikanski sabor piše

955
00:47:59,160 --> 00:48:00,660
 Isus nas je odkupio

956
00:48:00,660 --> 00:48:02,240
 svojom poslušnošću.

957
00:48:02,240 --> 00:48:04,580
 Ja sam osta šokiran

958
00:48:04,580 --> 00:48:05,980
 jer sam očekivao riječ

959
00:48:05,980 --> 00:48:06,600
 križ,

960
00:48:06,600 --> 00:48:07,780
 smrt,

961
00:48:07,780 --> 00:48:08,860
 krv,

962
00:48:08,860 --> 00:48:11,180
 znate kako ono mi razmišljamo.

963
00:48:11,180 --> 00:48:13,820
 Ali i smrt,

964
00:48:13,820 --> 00:48:14,640
 i križ,

965
00:48:14,640 --> 00:48:15,220
 i krv su

966
00:48:15,220 --> 00:48:17,020
 čin poslušnosti.

967
00:48:17,020 --> 00:48:18,860
 Bog otac je mogao zamisli

968
00:48:18,860 --> 00:48:19,880
 da Isus umre

969
00:48:19,880 --> 00:48:21,280
 tako da ga izbičuju

970
00:48:21,280 --> 00:48:22,320
 do smrti

971
00:48:22,320 --> 00:48:23,180
 i da se ne može

972
00:48:23,180 --> 00:48:23,860
 više digneti.

973
00:48:23,860 --> 00:48:25,100
 Mogao je

974
00:48:25,100 --> 00:48:26,040
 Bog otac zamisli

975
00:48:26,040 --> 00:48:26,760
 da Isus ode,

976
00:48:26,760 --> 00:48:28,040
 da žije 80 godina

977
00:48:28,040 --> 00:48:29,600
 i kao mudri starac kaže

978
00:48:29,600 --> 00:48:30,600
 sad ću umrijeti,

979
00:48:30,600 --> 00:48:32,020
 djeca moja čuvajte se

980
00:48:32,020 --> 00:48:33,520
 i sve što sam rekao čuvajte

981
00:48:33,520 --> 00:48:34,680
 i zaspe i ode.

982
00:48:34,680 --> 00:48:37,600
 Isus je umrao

983
00:48:37,600 --> 00:48:39,540
 kako je otac htio da umre.

984
00:48:40,380 --> 00:48:42,060
 I otac mu je govorio o tome,

985
00:48:42,060 --> 00:48:43,280
 pripremao ga na to

986
00:48:43,280 --> 00:48:44,800
 i dao mu milost

987
00:48:44,800 --> 00:48:45,500
 da to učini

988
00:48:45,500 --> 00:48:47,600
 i Isus je bio tome poslušan.

989
00:48:47,600 --> 00:48:49,200
 I gecemanije,

990
00:48:49,200 --> 00:48:50,660
 borba za poslušnost.

991
00:48:50,660 --> 00:48:54,220
 Isus se borio

992
00:48:54,220 --> 00:48:55,720
 da ostane u volji očevoj.

993
00:48:55,720 --> 00:48:57,780
 Nije bilo bitno

994
00:48:57,780 --> 00:48:58,360
 što je ispred

995
00:48:58,360 --> 00:48:59,000
 ili križ,

996
00:48:59,000 --> 00:48:59,720
 ili bić,

997
00:48:59,720 --> 00:49:00,800
 ili metak.

998
00:49:00,800 --> 00:49:02,400
 Sasvim je sve jedno.

999
00:49:02,400 --> 00:49:03,960
 Isus je htio

1000
00:49:03,960 --> 00:49:05,100
 ostati u volji očevoj.

1001
00:49:05,380 --> 00:49:07,440
 U svaki dan,

1002
00:49:07,440 --> 00:49:08,620
 svaki dan vašeg života

1003
00:49:08,620 --> 00:49:09,300
 Bog vas zove

1004
00:49:09,300 --> 00:49:10,460
 na molitvo i post,

1005
00:49:10,460 --> 00:49:13,240
 ali onda vi morate

1006
00:49:13,240 --> 00:49:14,160
 s njim razlučiti

1007
00:49:14,160 --> 00:49:15,240
 što je to

1008
00:49:15,240 --> 00:49:16,240
 na što vas on poziva.

1009
00:49:16,240 --> 00:49:18,420
 Neka će to bit

1010
00:49:18,420 --> 00:49:19,940
 osobna molitva

1011
00:49:19,940 --> 00:49:20,780
 godinu dana,

1012
00:49:20,780 --> 00:49:22,180
 nešto postiti nikad.

1013
00:49:22,180 --> 00:49:23,940
 I molitva će te izgrađivati.

1014
00:49:23,940 --> 00:49:25,440
 Onda će Bog doći reći

1015
00:49:25,440 --> 00:49:25,880
 moli mi,

1016
00:49:25,880 --> 00:49:27,420
 posti mi dva puta u tjednu,

1017
00:49:27,420 --> 00:49:28,360
 srijede i petke,

1018
00:49:28,360 --> 00:49:29,260
 na kruhu i vodi.

1019
00:49:29,260 --> 00:49:30,820
 I tih dana ćeš biti

1020
00:49:30,820 --> 00:49:31,900
 izrazito blagoslovjen.

1021
00:49:31,900 --> 00:49:33,540
 Ako ne budeš izrazito blagoslovjen

1022
00:49:33,540 --> 00:49:34,580
 nakon nekoliko vremena,

1023
00:49:34,640 --> 00:49:35,940
 pokušavaš određeno vrijeme

1024
00:49:35,940 --> 00:49:37,180
 da stekneš neki uzorak,

1025
00:49:37,180 --> 00:49:39,080
 onda razlučiš s nekim

1026
00:49:39,080 --> 00:49:39,740
 ko te prati

1027
00:49:39,740 --> 00:49:41,020
 ili ako te niko ne prati,

1028
00:49:41,020 --> 00:49:43,220
 skužiš da je loše

1029
00:49:43,220 --> 00:49:44,140
 da te niko ne prati

1030
00:49:44,140 --> 00:49:46,620
 i razlučiš da ne jaš plodove,

1031
00:49:46,620 --> 00:49:47,540
 očito u svom životu

1032
00:49:47,540 --> 00:49:48,600
 mijenja, dođi opet,

1033
00:49:48,600 --> 00:49:50,300
 baci se pred njegovo lice

1034
00:49:50,300 --> 00:49:51,640
 i traži njegovo vodstvo.

1035
00:49:51,640 --> 00:49:53,680
 Mi smo pozvani

1036
00:49:53,680 --> 00:49:55,020
 na konstantnu molitvu,

1037
00:49:55,020 --> 00:49:56,420
 to je isto odnos s gospodinom.

1038
00:49:56,420 --> 00:50:00,180
 Evo još neke stvari

1039
00:50:00,180 --> 00:50:02,420
 koje me Bog naučila,

1040
00:50:02,420 --> 00:50:03,460
 pa ću privoditi

1041
00:50:03,460 --> 00:50:04,880
 lagano stvari kraju.

1042
00:50:04,880 --> 00:50:07,420
 U postu me Bog učio

1043
00:50:07,420 --> 00:50:08,220
 da odgovornije

1044
00:50:08,220 --> 00:50:09,340
 pristupam vremenu

1045
00:50:09,340 --> 00:50:10,020
 i prehrani.

1046
00:50:10,020 --> 00:50:12,640
 Počeo me uči

1047
00:50:12,640 --> 00:50:13,680
 skroz nove vještine,

1048
00:50:13,680 --> 00:50:14,840
 nove poglede na stvari.

1049
00:50:14,840 --> 00:50:15,700
 Ti moraš unapred

1050
00:50:15,700 --> 00:50:16,720
 pripremati hranu,

1051
00:50:16,720 --> 00:50:17,460
 moraš razmišljaš

1052
00:50:17,460 --> 00:50:20,420
 što što što je na danijelu

1053
00:50:20,420 --> 00:50:21,120
 je neukusno

1054
00:50:21,120 --> 00:50:22,980
 i moraš ili skuhati

1055
00:50:22,980 --> 00:50:23,900
 ili u pećnicu.

1056
00:50:23,900 --> 00:50:25,340
 Nakon tri dana

1057
00:50:25,340 --> 00:50:26,460
 ti voće postane

1058
00:50:26,460 --> 00:50:27,760
 naporno,

1059
00:50:27,760 --> 00:50:29,080
 ne moš ga više jest toliko.

1060
00:50:29,080 --> 00:50:32,420
 I onda moraš početi

1061
00:50:32,420 --> 00:50:34,160
 disciplinirati,

1062
00:50:34,160 --> 00:50:34,920
 razmišljati

1063
00:50:34,920 --> 00:50:35,960
 o rasporedu danu

1064
00:50:35,960 --> 00:50:37,240
 i sad ove frikove

1065
00:50:37,240 --> 00:50:38,220
 koji u svijetu

1066
00:50:38,220 --> 00:50:39,600
 briju na tijelu

1067
00:50:39,600 --> 00:50:40,960
 i na zdravu prehranu

1068
00:50:40,960 --> 00:50:41,580
 i na izgled,

1069
00:50:41,840 --> 00:50:42,880
 oni to rade 10 puta

1070
00:50:42,880 --> 00:50:43,940
 bolje od

1071
00:50:43,940 --> 00:50:44,580
 valjda od

1072
00:50:44,580 --> 00:50:45,600
 prosečnog kršćanina

1073
00:50:45,600 --> 00:50:47,160
 koji želi postiti.

1074
00:50:47,160 --> 00:50:48,240
 Oni su ušli

1075
00:50:48,240 --> 00:50:48,640
 u neku

1076
00:50:48,640 --> 00:50:49,820
 duboku istinu

1077
00:50:49,820 --> 00:50:51,000
 kako se treba

1078
00:50:51,000 --> 00:50:51,680
 odnositi prema tijelu.

1079
00:50:51,680 --> 00:50:52,120
 Samo oni

1080
00:50:52,120 --> 00:50:54,400
 ulaze u idolatriju

1081
00:50:54,400 --> 00:50:55,080
 najčešće

1082
00:50:55,080 --> 00:50:56,700
 i pretjerivaju

1083
00:50:56,700 --> 00:50:57,940
 u neku krajnost.

1084
00:50:57,940 --> 00:50:59,120
 Evo, mene

1085
00:50:59,120 --> 00:51:00,020
 je Bog počeo učiti

1086
00:51:00,020 --> 00:51:00,900
 i onda ne samo

1087
00:51:00,900 --> 00:51:01,500
 da me uča

1088
00:51:01,500 --> 00:51:02,860
 da se disciplinira

1089
00:51:02,860 --> 00:51:04,000
 nego počeo mi je

1090
00:51:04,000 --> 00:51:06,000
 budi kreativnost

1091
00:51:06,000 --> 00:51:07,140
 i ja od jedan put

1092
00:51:07,140 --> 00:51:08,000
 počeo da dobivati

1093
00:51:08,000 --> 00:51:08,840
 želju

1094
00:51:08,840 --> 00:51:09,760
 da počnem kuhati.

1095
00:51:11,840 --> 00:51:13,000
 Muškarac koji kuha.

1096
00:51:13,000 --> 00:51:15,220
 Ja to nikad nema.

1097
00:51:15,220 --> 00:51:16,220
 Ja govorim ženi

1098
00:51:16,220 --> 00:51:17,260
 ovaj dan

1099
00:51:17,260 --> 00:51:18,220
 želim naučiti

1100
00:51:18,220 --> 00:51:19,440
 neko novo jelo kuhati.

1101
00:51:19,440 --> 00:51:20,900
 Želim ispeći

1102
00:51:20,900 --> 00:51:22,120
 prvi puh kolač u životu.

1103
00:51:22,120 --> 00:51:23,140
 Ono, počeli se javljati

1104
00:51:23,140 --> 00:51:23,580
 te misli.

1105
00:51:23,580 --> 00:51:24,440
 Vidim kreativnost

1106
00:51:24,440 --> 00:51:25,600
 mi je počela izlaziti.

1107
00:51:25,600 --> 00:51:27,120
